Package: cdmAcm0008
Title: Implementation of CDM Large-Scale Methodology ACM0008
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Supplies tidyverse-centric tooling to reproduce the consolidated Clean Development Mechanism methodology ACM0008 "Consolidated methodology for coal mine methane projects". The package contains helpers for applicability checks, equation-level computations, monitoring-period aggregation, and end-to-end emission reduction estimation alongside data simulation utilities tailored to methane capture and oxidation systems in underground coal mines.
